Class Restore

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
ArrayRestore
public class Restore
extends java.lang.Object
implements TrailElement

This TrailElement is the counterpiece for the xstore and the iinc instructions. It is generated when a local variables is changed. This can only happen when one of the following instructions is executed: astore, dstore, fstore, istore, lstore and iinc. It takes the information which local variable has to be restored, and what its original value was.
